    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305930/extras/d024bf14dfea8b3952ca22d7f1ab57bb.poster.avif?t=1746885382\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305930/extras/d024bf14dfea8b3952ca22d7f1ab57bb.webm?t=1746885382\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305930/extras/d024bf14dfea8b3952ca22d7f1ab57bb.mp4?t=1746885382\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Limbo Revolution is a first-person shooter set in a 1980s Eastern European City ravaged by war. In this haunting world, you play as a stalker, battling and surviving against bandits, other stalkers and the military.<br><br>With a rich, atmospheric setting and low poly graphics, this game transports you to a world of darkness and despair. Explore the desolate streets of the fallen city and face off against rouge military factions and bandits in intense battles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305930/extras/8a121527c5902557cd6f642a0fe3174a.poster.avif?t=1746885382\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305930/extras/8a121527c5902557cd6f642a0fe3174a.webm?t=1746885382\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305930/extras/8a121527c5902557cd6f642a0fe3174a.mp4?t=1746885382\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>As you progress through the game, you'll encounter a variety of weapons and tools to help you in your fight. From standard firearms to exotic western weapons from traders, you'll have everything you need to take on the enemy and survive.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305930/extras/b3e6890e875854c8360165bd3a1c3c51.poster.avif?t=1746885382\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305930/extras/b3e6890e875854c8360165bd3a1c3c51.webm?t=1746885382\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305930/extras/b3e6890e875854c8360165bd3a1c3c51.mp4?t=1746885382\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
